{"type": "article", "id": 11214, "title": "Segment Chairp-03午睡椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-25T07:27:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110846F2DpB1TtoY85vuPR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t2013 年毕业于首尔弘益大学木工与家具设计专业的设计师 <a href=\"http://www.saeromyoon.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sae-rom Yoon </a>设计了这套午睡椅，大大的壳状外壳让人可以舒服的蜷缩在里面，还配有一个符合人体工学的脚凳，每个都有厚厚的坐垫，看起来就很想窝着睡一下。Sae-rom Yoon 说小孩子都喜欢蜷缩身体在一个比较暗而且舒服的环境，是因为在母亲肚子里 10 个月都是这样的状态，所以要设计一个模拟母亲肚子也像是打开的贝壳的“椅子”，让人坐在里面或是躺着都感觉到舒适。（<a href=\"http://www.saeromyoon.com/?okay-portfolio=segment-chair_03\" target=\"_blank\">产品网站</a>）\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110844bA2wzRYZ8iCX1DFN.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1498\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110844UGItVda7MnH4whTr.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1499\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110844kUXK2Dao3hBO5gWd.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1498\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110845iF8WhDbKRTVmESkY.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"436\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span>\r\n\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n<span> </span>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n<span> </span>\r\n\t\t\r\n<span> </span>\r\n\t\r\n\n"}